{"sample_id": "coherence_fantasy_023", "genre": "western_fantasy", "difficulty": "medium", "input": {"preceding_context": "骑士雷欧被派去护送一位精灵使者穿越迷雾森林。森林中常有怪物出没。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "他们在森林中遇到了巨蜘蛛的袭击。雷欧奋勇战斗，但精灵使者用魔法轻松解决了蜘蛛。雷欧这才知道精灵使者的魔力远在自己之上。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 4, "rationale": "护送-危险-发现对方更强，有反转", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 4, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
