{"sample_id": "coherence_fantasy_025", "genre": "western_fantasy", "difficulty": "easy", "input": {"preceding_context": "小魔法师艾琳第一次使用飞行咒，结果飞到了树上下不来。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "她在树上待了三个小时，同学们在树下干着急。最后还是教授用悬浮咒把她接下来了。艾琳的脸红得像苹果。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 5, "rationale": "学咒-失败-尴尬-解决，有趣又真实", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 5, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
