{"sample_id": "coherence_fantasy_028", "genre": "western_fantasy", "difficulty": "medium", "input": {"preceding_context": "精灵公主偷偷溜出宫殿到人类集市上玩，她对什么都充满好奇。", "user_request": "请续写接下来的情节"}, "output": {"text": "她在集市上买了一个会唱歌的八音盒，还吃了人类做的棉花糖。结果她的尖耳朵在人群中太显眼了，被认了出来。护卫队赶来把她带回了宫殿。"}, "reference": {"coherence_score": 4, "rationale": "偷溜出门-新鲜体验-被发现-带回", "contradiction_types": [], "expected_behavior": ""}, "evaluation": {"narrative_coherence": 4, "plot_continuity": 5, "world_consistency": 5, "genre_fidelity": 5, "faithfulness": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "context_recall": 0.85}, "negative_sample": false, "error_type": null}
